{
  "stem": "25114.7",
  "chunk_idx": 13,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 8.6,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We went out, and Budapest wasn't like all the other countries-- already had open shops and lots of food and clothes.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And it was like-- Although a lot of-- Budapest ended actual the war-- the European war-- the last battles were in Budapest.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "A lot of houses were still burning.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "One part of it was absolutely undisturbed.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And beautiful shops with beautiful clothes, and markets were full of luscious fruit.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And we really gorged ourselves with everything.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "[LAUGHS] I went out and bought myself a beautiful dress and, for my husband, a suit.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "The first-- you can call 'civilian clothes,' because before that, we just had, you know, sort of make-- make up sort of-- made up of parachute silk, some blouses, and-- after the thing, some knitwear.",
      "word_count": 35
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "You know, what we could get.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And this was real stuff, you know?",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Lovely window shops-- absolutely beautiful.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And life and cafes and couples walking.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "This was, like, normal life.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "For us, it was something different.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "But we stayed there for three weeks.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "The only thing I didn't like in Budapest was the hot food.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "[LAUGHS] I always got burned.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Every time I took a mouthful, I was burned, it was so hot.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "But they liked hot food.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And then they took us to, from Budapest, another place which was close to the Austrian border.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "The Brigade-- the Zionist organization organized it all.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] And-- and they took-- took us from there to a place called Szentgotthard, which was on the border of a-- of a-- of Hungary and Austria.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And then we had to cross the Alps.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "On foot.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "With guides, of course.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "We had a guide.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And we had to climb right through the Alps, with special-- so-- because, at this time, the Russians were very close.",
      "word_count": 21
    }
  ],
